Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:07.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:11.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I hope you enjoy the miracle \Nof a ruby that guides someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:18.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief has issued \Nanother declaration of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:23.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This time, his target is the world's largest ruby,\N owned by the Hopper Magic Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:28.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. That sneak thief will never learn, \Nno matter how many times he's foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dummy. I return 'em on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,'Cause they're not the jewel I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Akako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:50.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That ruby is called a demon stone because \Nmisfortune comes to anyone who tries to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Red Tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:57.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But if Kid insists, then it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Red Tear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, that jewel is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:06.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:41.48,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Red Tear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori! Kid the Phantom Thief \Nsent out another advance notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:46.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We already got his advance notice yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:51.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said he's going to steal the world's \Nlargest ruby from the Hopper Magic Troupe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:55.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,during their dinner show at \Nthe Minato Hotel tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But this came today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,To My Dear Inspector Nakamori,\NDisregard what I said in yesterday's notice... \NPlease excuse my absence.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's calling it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you see the news this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kid the Phantom Thief \NConcedes an Early Defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is He on the Verge of Retiring?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:25.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. I oughta sue for libel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:30.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Jody Hopper, leader of the \NHopper Magic Troupe, comments:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"It's a shame I won't get \Nto see his magic." Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He must be scared of my Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a coward when it comes down to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:43.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jackass! Who could be afraid \Nof that third-rate inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a good reason for \Nnot stealing that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:52.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He just picked Aoko's pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,she got Aoko's wallet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And so fast, it made the first pickpocket \Nlook as subtle as a freight train!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:32.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Honestly. I heard the Japanese let pacifism \Nlull them into a sense of false security,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I didn't think it was this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:40.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you the leader of \Nthe Hopper Magic Troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jody Hopper-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:46.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's a magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No wonder she's got fast hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Remember, Kaito, she's in \Nthe news site's article...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:57.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Her grandfather is James Hopper,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,once the greatest magician in England!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:07.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,His father is Toichi Kuroba, \Nonce the greatest magician in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot. It's {\i1}the world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:17.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The world's foremost illusionist, \Nknown as the Magician of East Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:23.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But in the end, he and my grandfather \Nwere both like that pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:29.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just cunning swindlers who deceived people \Nand rolled them for their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:34.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But you do magic, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:39.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After my grandfather died two years ago, \NI had no choice but to inherit the troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But even so, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight is the \NHopper Magic Troupe's last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both of you, come and see it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you care to be tricked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,by swindlers like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:06.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The mysterious organization that \Nmurdered Dad eight years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So they're after it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Red Tear that Jody-san owns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:17.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Their objective is to obtain Pandora, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way are they gonna pass up \Nthe world's largest ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And after I canceled the \Nadvance notice for Dad's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you muttering \Nto yourself about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The movie's gonna start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Two people at the hotel entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,one in the revolving restaurant on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...three here at the dinner show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:51.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got detectives in the audience too, \Nbut... is he really not gonna show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so serious, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid's not coming tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So you should enjoy this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:12.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. Kaito was supposed \Nto come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:17.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way am I gonna see a show put on \Nby people who disrespect magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And so here I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How does the venue look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are three or four \Nplainclothes cops in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But we don't see anybody who could be Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Execute the plan in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And don't screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, Paul...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When did you get this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:20.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Probably because it's his last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not just Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:27.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The others are also going all out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,to improve their skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:34.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They want you to keep \Nthis magic troupe going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I already told you, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:43.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I took over, I gave you all two years \Nto find real jobs, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:47.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep the troupe going,\N you can do it yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...you're the only one who \Ncan keep us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:58.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of being in this world \Nof lies and deceit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides... I want this to be the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The last time I wear this accursed jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the leader, Jody-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then that's the world's biggest ruby, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you with the troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:31.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:34.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Does she always wear that jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's basically the trademark \Nof our magic troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:45.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, I didn't see Jody-san listed \Nas a performer in the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is she not very good at magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Heavens, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ever since my lady was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:57.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,her parents and grandfather, \NJames-san, taught her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so even now, she's the most talented \Nmagician in the whole troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So her parents perform magic, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They were a brilliant pair \Nin the world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Until they died ten years ago, \Nin an accident in the middle of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:22.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was the day James-sama was going to \Nretire and pass the jewel on to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ever since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:44.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...my lady has felt disdain for magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:52.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And since then, that ruby has been called \Na demon stone, bringer of misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Akako-chan \Nwas saying something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jody-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:04.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, for our finale, the Human Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How about letting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...take care of the show's finale?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:27.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What? He sent a note saying he wasn't coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You just can't trust a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Paul, take our lady to the dressing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We haven't killed anyone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to count to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:05.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to get hurt,\N give me that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Paul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to join him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Halt, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid shot at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You can have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...this jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mustn't, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:15.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give them the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Paul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm wearing a bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-Bulletproof vest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why would you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I'm really Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But Kid was out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was probably one of their accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:49.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A decoy to lure Inspector Nakamori and \Nthe other officers out of the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then what about Paul?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's been on the toilet \Nsince before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:14:00.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No wonder! I didn't think Paul \Nwas up to that level of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This Red Tear is your target, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I didn't think you were coming \Nafter you canceled the advance notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to steal that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I came here to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...both you and the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They escaped upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You guys get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:33.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That fraudulent bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! All right, try this on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:16.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She's not James Hopper's \Ngranddaughter for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:29.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to protect me and the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Minato Hotel\NRevolving Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, give me that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Her jewel isn't Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:04.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're the one \Nwho has nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I did a little tinkering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,with this restaurant's revolving mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And right as our guest is arriving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Snake-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kid. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:17.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But "Demon Stone" fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Because of this jewel, \Nmembers of the troupe were injured
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and the show was ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:28.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This really was the last performance \Nof the Hopper Magic Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:33.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With apologies to my grandfather, \Nit looks like I can finally be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:38.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Free from the world of magic that \Nrobbed my parents of their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And free from this cursed ruby, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But magic doesn't kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The jewel will tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:59.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, rubies are red, \Nbut that jewel is blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And its name is "Red Tear."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Red, a key word used to describe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather, James Hopper,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,left this to your world, his final...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,G-Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Papa... Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And me, when I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"My darling Jody..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You may despise magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:06.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,for killing your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:12.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just want you to recall once more
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:17.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the rush of excitement \Nyou felt when performing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,on stage the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the enthusiastic applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When this jewel glows red,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:37.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I pray that Jody Hopper, magic's gift \Nto the world, shall rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,James Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,G-Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:01.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He uses the jewel's refractive index \Nto make the glow of flames appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's projection magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh! Wow, he's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,To make a device like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:13.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. He calls it "Red Tear."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:18.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My magic mentor inserted it \Ninto the jewel for his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's very special magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I protected it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:32.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both of my parents \Nwere so proud of my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:41.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So you used to look like that \Nwhen performing magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give it one more shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...and the magic troupe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:58.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's this? You were curious \Nand came after all, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Pfft! I can do whatever they can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then do it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dummy. I'm done with tricks for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:18.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After the Red Tear, anything \NI did would pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:22.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:35.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A miracle called the Red Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:41.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Making that magic work requires the device, \Nknowing the trick, and one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Love embedded in the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:48.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:22.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito! Let's do the preview together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:27.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help you! The last \Npreview I did was popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do I care about popularity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:32.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the next episode, a mysterious \Nphantom thief in black appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It sounds like he has a duel with Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:36.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win... No, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:37.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid's gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:42.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Midnight Crow (Part One): \NThe Name is Corbeau the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Midnight Crow (Part One): \NThe Name is Corbeau the Phantom Thief!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:46.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way. Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion.
